Recovery Guaranteed 

Plastic surgery is a fine technique 

That has many great uses, 

Not the least of which could be 

The curing of credit-card abuses. 

-- Bud Stiller. 

Reconsider the Source 

Stress is healthful, experts say, 

And it has changed my attitude. 

I now can view my children 

With considerable gratitude. 

-- Mimi Kay. 

Daffynition 

Hiker's warning: cautionary trail. 

-- Daisy Brown. 

